lesson.title: Nanodegree Career Services
lesson.summary: The Careers team at Udacity is here to help you move forward in your career - whether it's finding a new job, exploring a new career path, or applying new skills to your current job.

atoms.text:
Youâ€™re probably in this Nanodegree program to advance your career - whether looking for a new job, learning new skills for your current job, or just exploring.

If you want career support during you program, career coaches provide personalized feedback on your resume, cover letter, LinkedIn profile, and GitHub.

You'll get honest, concise feedback from career coaches, including industry professionals.

atoms.caption: **Click on Career Services in the Classroom sidebar.**
atoms.alt: Career Services found in the Classroom sidebar.

atoms.text:
Join our [Careers channel](https://chat.udacity.com/rooms/community:hqb2c-b2a03e2d-0900-477f-beab-d7956cd29451) to connect with other job-seeking students, and get support from career coaches as you begin to search for your dream job! Receive daily career tips, resources, and stay up to date on all the [Career Events](https://www.udacity.com/events) Udacity offers.

The Udacity Careers team is here to help you figure out what you're looking for, plan for it, and work with you to move forward in your career. You can always contact us at [career-support@udacity.com](mailto:career-support@udacity.com).
